world.com/display_article/289410/12/none/none/Feat/QUANTUM-CASCADE-LASERS:-Quantum-cascade-lasers-enable-gas-sensing-technolog | accessdate            = 2008-01-25 | archive-date            = 2013-01-27 | archive-url            = https://archive.today/20130127164107/http://www.laserfocusworld.com/display_article/289410/12/none/none/Feat/QUANTUM-CASCADE-LASERS:-Quantum-cascade-lasers-enable-gas-sensing-technolog | dead-url            = yes }}</ref>和安全应用。 它们最终可用于在能见度差条件下的车辆[[巡航定速|巡航定速]]{{Citation needed|date=January 2008}}，防撞[[雷达|雷达]]{{Citation needed|date=January 2008}}，工业过程控制{{Citation needed|date=January 2008}}，和医疗诊断如呼吸分析仪<ref name="Hannemann"> {{Cite journal | last1            = Hannemann | first1           = M. | last2            = Antufjew | first2           = A. | last3            = Borgmann | first3           = K. | last4            = Hempel | first4           = F. | last5            = Ittermann | first5           = T. | last6            = Welzel | first6           = S. | last7            = Weltmann | first7           = K.D. | last8            = Völzke | first8           = H. | last9            = Röpcke | first9           = J.

